HEADWORD: Humifuse
<hw>Hu"mi*fuse</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>humus</ets> ground + <ets>fusus</ets>, p. p. of <ets>fundere</ets>
